{"tid":626604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[劍指臺獨] 中國海軍下周三於台灣海峽實彈射擊演習","createTime":"2018-04-12T09:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T09:19:49.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7446e55e0d1b20e0c05af9bc8b7f25c849fd48","tid":626604,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180412/bkncn-20180412165425892-0412_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180412%2Fbkncn-20180412165425892-0412_05011_001.html&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=12101354\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180412/bkncn-20180412165425892-0412_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海南三亞海事局周四（12日）通報，中國海軍於南海的軍事訓練提前結束，並撤銷日前發布的禁航令。同日，福建海事局發布航行警告，表示台灣海峽於下周三（18日）上午8時至翌日凌晨零時，於部分水域範圍內進行實彈射擊軍事演習，禁止所有船隻駛入。"},{"pid":"79871abfb0614e43a028502434bff4dc92b78a36","tid":626604,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"傻西共狗又想侵略台灣國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98c4160472f6740904ff7765c5caf6b8e9ebbb0","tid":626604,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"美國係南海曬馬<br />\n你就去台海演習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢同人鬥呀？"},{"pid":"5c7d3272378405ef07754371e05140e4c8237946","